1 Background

  • Why using Excel for data science?
    • Good for starter learning concept of data science
    • Great editor for 2-D data
    • Do not need coding background
    • Built-in tools, access from button
    • Visualizations
    • More
  • What is the advantage?
    • Graphic UI
    • More
  • What is the disadvantage?
    • Not good for big data
    • Not good for complex computation
    • Hard to automate
    • More

2.2.1 Home

  • Clipboard

    • Table boarder
    • Background color
    • Text color
  • Alignment
    • text wrapping
    • merge & un-merge cells
  • Number

    • Adding/removing format: money, time, percentage
  • Styles
    • Conditional formatting: data bar, color scale, customized rules
  • Cells
    • insert column to left, row to top
    • lock cell, lock sheet
    • hide column
    • adjust row height, column width

    • some commonly used functions
    • sort & order
